OL,3,CJersey health boss dismisses concerns
OL,4,Cabout toxic culture
OL,6,FThe Medical Director for Health and
OL,7,FCommunity Services (HCS) in Jersey has
OL,8,Fresponded to concerns about a toxic
OL,9,Fculture within the department after
OL,10,Fthree former senior health bosses
OL,11,Fshared a damning insight into it.
OL,13,FProfessor Simon Mackenzie, Tom Hayhoe
OL,14,Fand Hugo Mascie-Taylor spoke at three
OL,15,Fpublic hearings organised by Jersey's
OL,16,FHealth and Social Security (HSS)
OL,17,FScrutiny Panel this week.
