OL,3,CJersey health boss dismisses concerns
OL,4,Cabout toxic culture
OL,6,FTogether they raised fears over
OL,7,Fpatient safety, a toxic working
OL,8,Fculture within the service and a
OL,9,Fresistance to change.
OL,11,FPatrick Armstrong, Medical Director
OL,12,Ffor Jersey, told ITV News: "I see
OL,13,Fsignificant improvements in all
OL,14,Fdepartments.
OL,16,F"There is a perception that people
OL,17,Fdon't bring concerns forward but I
OL,18,Fsee, every single week, people
OL,19,Fbringing concerns forward."
