OL,3,CJersey health boss dismisses concerns
OL,4,Cabout toxic culture
OL,6,FProfessor Simon Mackenzie and Tom
OL,7,FHayhoe also said they were reluctant
OL,8,Fto receive care in Jersey due to the
OL,9,Fstate of the service.
OL,11,FHowever, Mr Armstrong said: "I would
OL,12,Fchoose to be treated here. When you
OL,13,Fare looking for issues within an
OL,14,Forganisation you will find them.
OL,16,F"I see those issues, I completely
OL,17,Facknowledge them but I also see the
OL,18,Fhuge care and the huge amount of work
OL,19,Fthat everyone in this organisation
OL,20,Fdoes. We're striving to make it
OL,21,Fbetter."
