OL,3,CJersey health boss dismisses concerns
OL,4,Cabout toxic culture
OL,6,FMr Armstrong also reiterated that his
OL,7,Fdepartment is following guidance
OL,8,Fsupplied by The National Institute for
OL,9,FHealth and Care Excellence (NICE).
OL,11,F"What we have also said is that we
OL,12,Fwill listen if clinicians feel that
OL,13,Fthere is better guidance such as
OL,14,FEuropean guidance or American guidance
OL,15,Fthat may be more up-to-date.
OL,17,F"What I would not tolerate is people
OL,18,Fnot following any guidance at all."
