OL,6,FMr Armstrong said he thinks the
OL,7,Fculture within the organisation has
OL,8,Fchanged but that there is work to do.
OL,10,FHe added: "I believe that I have
OL,11,Fhelped oversee a lot of significant
OL,12,Fchange already."
